<https://colonial-heritage.triply.cc/nmvw/id/object/7106-472> <https://colonialcollections.nl/schema#name> "Ngalajiyi, Ngapa, Ngarlkirdi Jukurrpa - Bush Carrot, Water and Witchetty Grub Dreaming" .
